		<descript>
			<langdata>eng</langdata>
			<abstract>This is a scanned version of the 1764 paper map entitled: Carte de l'entree du Gange et Son Cours Jusqua Ugli Carte de l'entre de la Riviere d'Aracam.  The map was scanned at 300 dots per inch and is in the TIFF format. Thanks to Prof. Frances Pritchett, Columbia University, for providing the original paper map for this scan.</abstract>
			<purpose>Scanned maps may be used for a variety of purposes.</purpose>
<supplinf>1map ; 28.5 x 23.5 cm.

Pagination : Tome III, n 41./ Pagination corresponds to the  "Petit atlas maritime" / Jacques Nicolas Bellin, Paris : Bellin, [ca] 1764, in 5 volumess d'aprs le National maritime museum cat., vol. 3, p. 248.</supplinf>
